    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205560/extras/3d41cc1c92309f98ef0709844ea2cf41.poster.avif?t=1763820296\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205560/extras/3d41cc1c92309f98ef0709844ea2cf41.webm?t=1763820296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205560/extras/3d41cc1c92309f98ef0709844ea2cf41.mp4?t=1763820296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能爬多远？加入 JanKenUP！电梯并检查出来。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✊ 在乘坐没有最高楼层的电梯时玩石头、纸和剪刀。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205560/extras/db5c13d486db6aafb00879f19c90948c.poster.avif?t=1763820296\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205560/extras/db5c13d486db6aafb00879f19c90948c.webm?t=1763820296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205560/extras/db5c13d486db6aafb00879f19c90948c.mp4?t=1763820296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🖐 单人游戏：解锁所有角色，打破记录并获得所有可用成就。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205560/extras/cf8d7869010e66e7aeb6891a370b5878.poster.avif?t=1763820296\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205560/extras/cf8d7869010e66e7aeb6891a370b5878.webm?t=1763820296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205560/extras/cf8d7869010e66e7aeb6891a370b5878.mp4?t=1763820296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✌ 本地多人游戏：最多支持8名玩家，一决胜负，看看谁是最强的（需要操纵杆）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205560/extras/32e877195d8aa008918494551fa01f95.poster.avif?t=1763820296\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205560/extras/32e877195d8aa008918494551fa01f95.webm?t=1763820296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205560/extras/32e877195d8aa008918494551fa01f95.mp4?t=1763820296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
